  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK894">
<l>kūṟṟattaik kaiyāl viḷittaṟṟā lāṟṟuvārk</l>
<l>kāṟṟātā riṉṉā ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The weak doing evil to the strong is like beckoning Yama to come (and destroy them).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
